  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>The purpose of this hearing was to examine China‚Äôs domestic and international clean energy policies, as well as the state of U.S.-China cooperation on clean energy, in order to provide recommendations to Congress.</p>

<p><i>The following are short summaries and links to the testimony of the six ChinaFAQs experts:</i></p></div>
