                <span class="field-content"><a href="../blog-posts/china‚%2580%2599s-new-regional-air-quality-regulations-win-win-local-air-quality-and-climate">China‚Äôs New Regional Air Quality Regulations: A Win-Win for local air quality and the climate</a></span>
  </div>
  
  <div class="views-field-field-image-fid">
                <span class="field-content"><img src="../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/Nanjing_View.png" alt="" title="" width="189" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/></span>
